                What you would be dealing with with mlAuth.
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                <span class="font-semibold line-through">Nothing from the previous list.</span>
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Spend your valuable time and energy working on the most important aspects of your app.
